data.description: Amazing home on a large corner lot in Devonshire! You are greeted by gorgeous hardwood floors in the living areas of the first floor. The home office at the front of the home is private and perfect for working from home. Also, in the front of the home is a formal dining room. The open living room and kitchen are open to the upstairs game room. The kitchen is a chef's delight with a gas cooktop, plenty of granite counter space, beautiful chocolate cabinets, and a pantry. The living room features a gorgeous gas fireplace. The owner's suite has wood floors, a vaulted ceiling, and a great view of the backyard. The ensuite has an oversized shower with a bench, plus a garden tub and dual sinks. There are three other bedrooms that all share a bathroom. The upstairs game room or additional living space has a half bath, making this space very flexible. Outside you will enjoy summer evenings under the HUGE covered patio. So many great features. Beautiful Altura energy efficient home.
